07:23.068 --> 07:24.866
I was studying to
be an antiquarian

07:24.945 --> 07:26.743
of ancient artifacts.

07:26.821 --> 07:29.244
Now I never believed in the
supernatural stuff myself,

07:29.324 --> 07:31.747
just had a fascination
with superstitions.

07:31.826 --> 07:33.453
But everything changed

07:33.536 --> 07:36.255
