07:44.798 --> 07:46.175
After purchasing this crown

07:46.257 --> 07:48.555
from an old dock worker
in northern Scandinavia,

07:48.635 --> 07:51.104
I brought it home and excitedly
showed my fiancee, Betty.

07:51.179 --> 07:52.772
I jokingly put it on my head,

07:52.847 --> 07:54.474
just for a laugh or something,

07:54.557 --> 07:56.935
and that's when it started...
the visions.

07:57.018 --> 07:58.770
